{"type":"message","id":"7bc58ce7","parentId":"ffb4c304","timestamp":"2026-06-27T03:09:46.483Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both MCP services are down. The 小红书 MCP is missing cookies, and MediaCrawler MCP isn't running. Since both are unavailable, I can't fetch the travel content as planned.\n\nI should report this failure via the cron job's delivery mechanism. The cron job has an announce delivery - but wait, this is the cron task execution itself. Let me just report the failure to the user.\n\nSince the cron job is configured to announce, the text I return here will go to the channel. Let me summarize the"},{"type":"text","text":"两项小红书 MCP 服务均不可用，导致推送任务失败：\n\n1. **小红书 MCP（端口 18060）** — 已重启，但缺少登录 Cookie（`cookies.json` 不存在），搜索接口返回超时/空数据\n2. **MediaCrawler MCP（端口 18080）** — 连接被拒，可能未启动\n\n**建议处理方式：**\n- 需要在端口 18060 的容器内重新扫码登录小红书账号以获取 Cookie\n- 或者启动 MediaCrawler MCP 并完成小红书平台的登录认证\n\n今天的旅游推送暂时无法执行，需要先修复 MCP 服务的登录状态。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782529778691}}
